
How to create a statefull widget.

1)Create a class that extends statefull widget.
2)OverRide createState Method.
  createState method accepts State Object<> as return type.
3)Create a class that extends state. (we are use _for private).
4)OverRide build method.

How to get the updated state of the widget.
*******************************************

To get the updated state of the widget.
use  setState(() {}) method.


DisAdvantage of StateFull Widget.
********************************
When ever we use a setState than entire widget will be build again.
Which is bad for application which has mulitple widget.

So statefull widget have this drawback.